33:13.964 --> 33:15.364
Scott.

33:16.394 --> 33:18.078
Just listen.

33:18.112 --> 33:21.598
I can't pretend
that I'm not happy

33:21.633 --> 33:23.600
that my first play
was done at Lincoln Center.

33:23.635 --> 33:26.570
But if I'm
being honest,

33:26.621 --> 33:30.457
I knew
what I did hurt you.

33:30.475 --> 33:32.709
And instead of apologizing
back then,

33:32.744 --> 33:37.347
I told myself
that it wasn't really that bad.

33:37.382 --> 33:40.617
So here I am,

33:40.652 --> 33:43.804
15 years too late,

33:43.838 --> 33:48.041
saying I'm sorry.

33:48.076 --> 33:52.429
Thanks.

33:52.463 --> 33:56.483
Hey, Jules.

33:56.517 --> 33:58.502
I heard about your split
from Frank.

33:58.536 --> 34:01.388
I remember...

34:01.422 --> 34:05.292
How in love you both were.

34:05.326 --> 34:07.294
I'm sorry.

34:15.402 --> 34:19.656
[Rock music playing]

34:19.690 --> 34:22.042
You're right.
We're cowards.

34:22.076 --> 34:23.143
What are you
talking about?

34:23.161 --> 34:24.328
Using that bathroom
is the bravest thing

34:24.362 --> 34:25.462
I've done in weeks.

34:25.496 --> 34:27.080
I had to make mittens
out of paper towels.

34:27.098 --> 34:28.415
I'm crazy about him.

34:28.449 --> 34:31.652
Seeing him perform today
made it so clear.

34:31.686 --> 34:32.902
Even right now,
watching him

34:32.937 --> 34:35.639
hit on that guy
for Kyle has me all...

34:35.672 --> 34:38.257
Melty.

34:38.292 --> 34:40.577
- Then tell him.
- He's not into me.

34:40.610 --> 34:41.712
Then you'll know.

34:41.746 --> 34:45.098
And you'll cry,
and you'll hate him,

34:45.132 --> 34:46.650
and then
you'll move on.

34:46.684 --> 34:49.319
At least you
put yourself out there.

34:49.370 --> 34:52.371
I'm scared.

34:52.406 --> 34:55.192
What if I put myself
out there first?

35:00.998 --> 35:02.599
Hey, you.

35:02.633 --> 35:04.334
Look alive.

35:04.369 --> 35:06.203
[Cymbals crash]

35:06.237 --> 35:09.606
Derek Wills,
I am the one.

