35:32.363 --> 35:36.533
♪ I'd drink beer
with the guys ♪

35:38.703 --> 35:44.674
♪ and chase
after girls ♪

35:44.709 --> 35:47.878
♪ I'd make out
with who I wanted ♪

35:47.929 --> 35:51.181
♪ and never get busted
for it ♪

35:51.215 --> 35:54.017
♪ 'cause they'd
stick up for me ♪

35:54.051 --> 35:59.189
♪ if I were a boy

35:59.223 --> 36:06.062
